brewery.name: Airways Brewing Company
brewery.description:
Friendly service and tasty beer make us a favorite of locals as well as beer enthusiasts from all over. 

Special and seasonal beers make a frequent appearance. Our tap room has bar seating as well as small tables. On sunny days, garden seating is available.

Airways opened on March 4, 2010. Founder and brewer Alex Dittmar has had a lifelong passion for 60â€²s era jetliners. Airways is a combination of his love for airplanes, good beer, and a connection with people from all over the world.
